sections.heading: of Nebraska at Omaha; laws applicable
sections.text: Chapter 85, articles 1, 4, and 5, relating to the Board of Regents and the University of Nebraska shall be applicable to the University of Nebraska at Omaha except as modified or limited by section 85-192.SourceLaws 1967, c. 620, ยง 13, p. 2082;Laws 1978, LB 756,
